@startuml
title Room Database – Entity Relationship Diagram

skinparam linetype ortho

entity "users" as Users {
  * **localId** : INTEGER <<PK, autoGenerate>>
  --
  * userId    : TEXT      <<UUID>>
  * fullName  : TEXT      <<UNIQUE>>
  * embedding : BLOB      <<128 × FLOAT32 = 512 bytes>>
}

note right of Users
  Encrypted at rest via SQLCipher
  (passphrase from DatabasePassphraseProvider).

  embedding stored as little-endian ByteArray.
  Cosine similarity computed in-app at runtime.
end note

@enduml
